</P>
<P>
	Pavol Demitra and Michal Handzus also scored for St. Louis,  
which won its second in a row to improve to 2-2-0-0. Doug Weight 
and Ryan Smyth scored for the Oilers (1-2-1-1). 
</P>
<P>
