to the net, fell in the crease and St. Louis captain Sean Pronger 
pushed the puck behind McLennan at 8:13 of the second. 
</P>
<P>
	Handzus clinched the win with 2:26 left in the third on a weak  
backhander in a shorthanded situation. 
</P>
<P>
	St. Louis defensemen Al MacInnis and Ricco Persson left in the  
second period and didn't return. 
</P>
<P>
	MacInnis has an ankle contusion after blocking a shot and is to  
be examined when the team returns to St. Louis. Persson has a 
strained knee. 
  	   	
