<HEADLINE> Captain Steve Wins Keeneland Race </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LEXINGTON, Ky. (AP) -- Captain Steve took the lead from the start  
and pulled away for a three-length victory Sunday in the $442,000 
Lane's End Breeders' Futurity at Keeneland. 
</P>
