	While Michael Irvin lay motionless with head and neck injuries  
and teammates knelt in prayer, many of the 66,669 at Veterans 
Stadium cheered -- first when realizing Irvin was down, then again 
when paramedics wheeled a stretcher onto the field. 

</P>
