strained hip flexor, and he caught five passes for 62 yards. ... 
Arizona's defense was bolstered in a 14-3 victory over the New York 
Giants by the return of two-time Pro Bowl tackle Eric Swann, who 
played for the first time in nearly a year after two operations on 
his arthritic right knee. 

</P>
